headline: Keysight Recognized for Corporate Social Responsibility Efforts
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., December 10, 2025--Keysight announced the company has received multiple awards and recognitions for its corporate social responsibility (CSR) efforts throughout 2025.

headline: Assessing Keysight Technologies (KEYS) Valuation After Its Strong Recent Share Price Rally
summary: Keysight Technologies (KEYS) has quietly put together an impressive run, with the stock up about 15% over the past month and more than 20% in the past 3 months. See our latest analysis for Keysight Technologies. That recent burst of buying sits on top of a strong backdrop, with a roughly 31% year to date share price return and a 25% one year total shareholder return suggesting momentum is building as investors warm to Keysight’s growth profile and valuation.
